{"tid":1414751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞將正式向PSG提出買回尼馬","createTime":"2019-08-05T12:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:25:46.000Z","uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9cab5033c963dc5fe78d9d59c252cea5aa0cdf","tid":1414751,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"雖然尼馬已返回PSG操練一段時間，但至今未有在熱身賽上陣1分鐘，即使球隊周六在法冠盃以2︰1擊敗雷恩一仗，他亦只坐在觀眾席睇波。<br />\n<br />\n事實上尼馬打算返回巴塞的新聞在今夏沒完沒了，據了解巴塞快將正式向PSG提出斟介，雖然後者無意放人，但隨著法甲將在下星期展開，PSG亦深明勉強留人對更衣室氣氛沒有好處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VaZT3pA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVaZT3pA.jpg&h=d169137e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過鑑於PSG即使放人亦要收回當日收購尼馬的2.22億歐元轉會費，巴塞亦需先賣人套現，繼剛以4,500萬歐元把前鋒馬爾甘售予辛尼特後，中場拉芬拿艾簡達拿亦快將離隊，而古天奴和拿傑迪錫亦是可能被放走的球員。"},{"pid":"6d6f5e6d603ffe48ee60821326aad874b17021e1","tid":1414751,"uid":51848,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4wWgK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4wWgK1.png&h=bacfa354&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79227be138766b19f1012ec84b716e1bd54f6b5f","tid":1414751,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:46:50.000Z","msg":"麥巴比：希望尼馬留在PSG<br />\n<br />\n巴黎聖日耳門皇牌前鋒基利安麥巴比，正於中國備戰法冠盃對雷恩。麥巴比向傳媒表示，希望尼馬會繼續留在PSG，和他並肩作戰爭取所有冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2j8Siv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2j8Siv.jpg&h=bb593e70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46f503bf45b471d9d3e06b33577b1cd6f6c8805a","tid":1414751,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"C朗拿度估計尼馬留效PSG<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ug6Szxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fug6Szxg.jpg&h=22844009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼馬一直想離開PSG重返巴塞隆拿，只是始終未見有轉會安排出現，他有可能最終繼續效力PSG。<br />\n<br />\nC朗拿度指出，他認為尼馬最終會選擇留隊：「尼馬傳過會去巴塞、皇馬及祖雲達斯，我也不知道最終結果，等傳媒去發掘。但我認為尼馬會留在PSG，如果不是這樣，他會去令他感到快樂的球隊。」"},{"pid":"a8c3a7a3049e533b92bf57c966db7b546b21d21c","tid":1414751,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/H4wWgK1.png[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4wWgK1.png%5Bimg%5D&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=780ba3ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/H4wWgK1.png[img]</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079ffb9d395df418cbc95da2eba7d5d0381fbf03","tid":1414751,"uid":202362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"6d6f5e6d603ffe48ee60821326aad874b17021e1","tid":1414751,"uid":51848,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4wWgK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4wWgK1.png&h=bacfa354&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"事實勝於雄辯<br />\n鳩蛇不如把握機會休息吓  唔好開po<br />\n你都成日ot 瞓覺時間又冇得瞓"},{"pid":"4d0e2fabf276603c28b13fd179aa76e9ad774b77","tid":1414751,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"079ffb9d395df418cbc95da2eba7d5d0381fbf03","tid":1414751,"uid":202362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"6d6f5e6d603ffe48ee60821326aad874b17021e1","tid":1414751,"uid":51848,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H4wWgK1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH4wWgK1.png&h=bacfa354&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"事實勝於雄辯<br />\n鳩蛇不如把握機會休息吓  唔好開po<br />\n你都成日ot 瞓覺時間又冇得瞓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"Hi鳩蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f5496336acd081f0ca3022d4c982d241